This paper discusses the design and implementation of a software component for solving elliptic PDEs using multilevel preconditioners, which is relevant to numerical analysis (cs.NA), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), modeling and simulation (cs.MS), computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE), and scientific computing (cs.SC).
